# Images

Sprite sheets, textures, and background images.

## Recommended Files

### Player Assets
- player_ship.png - Player mecha sprite
- player_bullets.png - Player projectiles
- player_thrust.png - Engine thrust animation

### Enemy Assets
- enemy_small.png - Small enemies
- enemy_medium.png - Medium enemies
- enemy_large.png - Large enemies
- boss_sprites.png - Boss sprites

### Effects
- explosions.png - Explosion sprite sheet
- particles.png - Particle textures
- powerups.png - Power-up sprites

### Backgrounds
- bg_stars.png - Starfield background
- bg_nebula.png - Nebula layer
- bg_planet.png - Planet graphics

Place your sprite files here and ask @assets to load them!
